--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Name   : zfs_stats_lite
Type   : Ansible role

Authors: liv community
License: Simplified BSD License

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DESCRIPTION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

zfs-stats displays ZFS statistics in human-readable format including
ARC, L2ARC, zfetch (DMU) and vdev cache statistics.

For more information on the usage and available configuration options,
consult the following sections.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
USAGE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

INSTALL
  - hosts: all
    roles:
      - role: zfs_stats_lite
    vars:
      zfs_stats_lite_state: 'install'

REMOVE
  - hosts: all
    roles:
      - role: zfs_stats_lite
    vars:
      zfs_stats_lite_state: 'remove'

INACTIVE
  - hosts: all
    roles:
      - role: zfs_stats_lite
    vars:
      zfs_stats_lite_state: 'inactive'

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
PARAMETERS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ROLE
  zfs_stats_lite_state
    Description: Control the state of the role.
    Implemented: 0.1
    Required   : False
    Value      : Predetermined
    Type       : String
    Default    : 'install'
    Options    :
      Install : 'true' | 'yes' | 'install'
      Remove  : 'false' | 'no' | 'remove'
      Inactive: 'quiesce' | 'inactive'

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
CONFLICTS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ROLES
  zfs_stats_lite

